I am an FFL Dealer who works out of my home and carry no inventory.  And because I don't carry any inventory,  I can generally save you money compared to the big box store sporting goods store.  If you are looking for a particular firearm; email, call, or text me with what you are looking for with the manufacturer, model, caliber, and even a upc or item number from the manufacturer website and I will quote you a out the door price that includes the gun, shipping, markup, background check and sales tax.  In otherwords, this is all you would pay.  I also have a full time professional career and do this on the side so if I don't get back to you immediately just keep that in mind but generally I can asher you in a short time and always on the same day.  So, with that in mind, I look forward to working with you, and helping you with all of your firearm needs!
 
First step is if you agree to the price that I give you is to give me the go ahead to order the firearm that you want.  No down payment is needed!  I accept cash, check, money orders and can now do credit cards!  (Additional 2% added to total bill for credit card orders)  Once your firearm comes in generally within 2-4 business days in most cases, you come to complete the background check and pay for your firearm.  Background checks are done right away which means as long as you pass you get to leave with your firearm right away!  Thanks for looking...
Chad 
Days End Firearm Sales
Marshfield,  WI. 54449
